{"name":"Champion","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"lawful good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"breastplate","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"16 (studded leather, shield)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"112 (15d8 + 45)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"15","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The gladiator can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The gladiator regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the gladiator can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the gladiator can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The gladiator can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the gladiator's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the gladiator's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the gladiator dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Brave","desc":"The [MON] has advantage on saving throws against being frightened."},{"name":"Brute","desc":"A melee weapon deals one extra die of its damage when the [MON] hits with it (included in the attack)."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes three melee attacks or two ranged attacks."},{"name":"Warhammer","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 2D8] bludgeoning damage, or [STR 2D10] bludgeoning damage if used with two hands."},{"name":"Shield Bash","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +7 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. _Hit:_ 9 (2d4 + 4) bludgeoning damage. If the target is a Medium or smaller creature, it must succeed on a DC 15 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Goad (3/day)","desc":"The [MON] yells at a creature within range which can understand it. The target makes a DC [CON SAVE] wisdom save or else it has disadvantage to attack any creature except the [MON]."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}